title: Fake Love

description.plain: “Fake Love” finds Drake criticizing friends and associates who only show him love because of his incredible success. He identifies their false emotions and explains how he deals with them. The song was released during Drake’s birthday episode of OVO Sound Radio.

embed_content: Read “Fake Love” by Drake on Genius
